snippet.title: Sega GT 2002 - Trailer - OXM 2
snippet.description:
From Official Xbox Magazine Disc 2, January 2002
Trailer for Sega GT 2002 from SEGA
Captured via XSplit Broadcaster
Original disc BIK files are in a stacked interlaced format that don't convert with RADGameTools or ffmpeg. If you have a solution to convert these files please contact me.
Releases Page: http://vgpavilion.com/games/2002/sega-gt-2002/
